            description: "A continuation of Chem 5610. Catabolism and anabolism of carbohydrates, lipids, proteins, and nucleic acids. Photosynthesis, oxidative phosphorylation and membranes.  Credit may not be given for both Chem 5620 and Chem 4620.  Prerequisite: Chem 4610 or 5610.",
